process_user_data.description: Processes user data and returns formatted result

validate_input.description: Validates input data and returns validation result
validate_input.code: def validate_input(data): return {'valid': True, 'errors': []} if data else {'valid': False, 'errors': ['No data provided']}

calculate_total.description: Calculates total from a list of numbers
calculate_total.code: def calculate_total(numbers): return sum(numbers) if numbers else 0
